headline: J.B. Hunt Transport Services, Inc. Announces Third Quarter 2025 Earnings Release Date and Conference Call Information
summary: LOWELL, Ark., October 01, 2025--J.B. Hunt Transport Services expects to issue third quarter 2025 earnings at the close of the market Wednesday, October 15, 2025.
